explain basic select /*+ parallel(lyq_test 4) */ COL_INT from lyq_test where PK  in (1,3,5,7) group by COL_INT having COL_INT not in (10,9) order by COL_INT;
Query Plan
========================================
|ID|OPERATOR                  |NAME    |
----------------------------------------
|0 |PX COORDINATOR MERGE SORT |        |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR      |:EX10000|
|2 |  └─SORT                  |        |
|3 |    └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR   |        |
|4 |      └─TABLE GET         |LYQ_TEST|
========================================
