|ID|OPERATOR                                    |NAME                       |
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |PX COORDINATOR                              |                           |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR                        |:EX10001                   |
|2 |  └─HASH DISTINCT                           |                           |
|3 |    └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR                     |                           |
|4 |      └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)           |:EX10000                   |
|5 |        └─HASH DISTINCT                     |                           |
|6 |          └─NESTED-LOOP SEMI JOIN           |                           |
|7 |            ├─PX BLOCK ITERATOR             |                           |
|8 |            │ └─TABLE RANGE SCAN            |LYQ_TEST(INDEX_LYQ_TEST_T7)|
|9 |            └─SUBPLAN SCAN                  |VIEW1                      |
|10|              └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE RANGE SCAN|LYQ_TEST(INDEX_LYQ_TEST_T3)|
=============================================================================
